metadata.name: Aries ♈️
metadata.description:
Born between March 21 - April 19, Aries signifies leadership. 

In a women, she may come off naive or selfish, however she is full of energy and power. An Aries is most likely to be attracted to speed and competition, as they always try to be first in everything (from their work to social gatherings).

In fact, it is in their nature to take action, even sometimes before they think about it. 

As for love, Aries has a desire of fire. They feel the need to take initiative; and when they do fall in love, they express their love to that person without even giving it a second thought.

Overall, Aries have a strong sense of personality and leadership and have a little sense of emotional control.

🐏 Animal: Ram
🪐Ruler: Mars
🔥Element: Fire

Resolution: 3000 x 4000 Px
Artists: Mehdi Basirat X Pailin Mirault
